des:
Control your smart devices after connecting Alexa to your ALFA DYSER products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our " ALFA DYSER" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one ALFA DYSER account in our " ALFA DYSER" app;
(3). You need to have some ALFA DYSER devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " ALFA DYSER" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "ALFA DYSER" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "ALFA DYSER" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "ALFA DYSER", and you'll be navigated to ALFA DYSER login page;
(9). Input your ALFA DYSER account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on Robot Vacuum.”
“Alexa,turn off Robot Vacuum.”
